{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, look, not only did my husband save your life and did you a lot of good, but he also saved your sister's life.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's not more than fair that you should come to testify in his behalf.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these old timers, so to say-- and she was one of them, and my friend, this Maurice-- they had a-- like a group of people where they would meet every week and talk about concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was all their discussion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a club reminiscing old stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had a meeting-- and they wanted in that general meeting-- they wanted to discuss what do we do?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Should she go, should she not go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like-- you know, like a board of directors discussing is it the right thing, or is it the wrong thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, do you have an obligation to go testify and save somebody's life, maybe, a guy who-- who-- I don't know exactly what they had against him, but if they took him to court, they must have had against him something that was serious.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they decided that she should not go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she, on her own, decided to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my friend, Maurice, and she-- they were all paid by the German government, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went there to-- he was testifying against.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was testifying in behalf.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, he apparently got off with a-- with a small jail term.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because she was, like, pleading the court, look, he saved my sister's life, and she--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was kept a secret for many years in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
